{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_HandLower}}
'''A_HandLower'''

(no parameters)

This codepointer lowers the HUD sprite, after it has reached the bottom of the screen, the graphic is cleared.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|StrifePlayer}} and actors inheriting from it.

